    <description>19012024 Jasmin/Ceili: When Opportunity is created with value in Services in Portfolio, Opportunity Products with no price are created based on Product name that matches the value name.
09022024 Jasmin/Ceili: Post migration version. If Is New or Trigger Sync decision added. Runs only on new opps and opps Trigger Sync value is updated to 2024.
14022024 Jasmin/Ceili: Price Book Entry filter added to get records. Currency = Opp currency.
06052024 Atte/Ceili: Automation enabled check added to entry conditions</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>forIsNew</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>ISNEW()</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>forSingleService</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF(
CONTAINS({!varServicesInPortfolio}, &quot;;&quot;),
TRIM(                                                                                                         
SUBSTITUTE(
LEFT( {!varServicesInPortfolio} , FIND(&quot;;&quot;,  {!varServicesInPortfolio} )),
&quot;;&quot;,                                                                                          
&quot;&quot;)),
{!varServicesInPortfolio})</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>forUpdatedServicesInPortfolio</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF(
CONTAINS({!varServicesInPortfolio}, &quot;;&quot;),
MID({!varServicesInPortfolio},FIND(&quot;;&quot;,
{!varServicesInPortfolio})+1,LEN({!varServicesInPortfolio})-
LEN(LEFT({!varServicesInPortfolio}, FIND(&quot;;&quot;,{!varServicesInPortfolio})))+1),
&quot;&quot;)</expression>
    </formulas>
